         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245"><!-- p3l5-r10 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Hd1e108">Rubrica 10</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Hd1e111" type="question-title">Cum quibus non sit loquendum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>¶ Cum quibus sit loquen
      <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>dum. Rubrica. 10 <!--193.xml-->
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e123">
               <pb ed="#V" n="77-v"/>
               <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>CRonica de nugis philo
      <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>sophorum. c. 8
      <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e136">ilicet de periandro. Periander corin
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>thius: vnus de septem sapiententibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>ait: verborum infandorum enunciationem
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>ne facias. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e146">
               <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e150">¶ Socrates in exhortationibus. c. 2. Que ne
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>phas est agere: eadem neque fari bonum exi
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>stimes. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e159">
               <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e163">¶ Aristotelis polyticorum: lib. 7. c. 12. et fina.
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>Ex dicere de facili quodcunque turpium: fit
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>et ipsum facere turpe. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e175">¶ Paulus apostolus epistola. in ad corsnthi
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>os. c. 25. et p. Corrumpunt bonos mores fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>bulationes pessime vel colloquia mala.
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum. li. 19. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>8. Ubicunque videris orationem corruptam
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>P lacere: ibi quoque mores a recto destituis
        <lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>se non erit dubium. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e192"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e194"> Idem de moribus:
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>Turpia ne dixeris. paulatim enim pudor re
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>rum per verba dediscitur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e202">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e206">¶ Maximianus: Contractata diu crimina
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>crimen habent </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e212">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e216">¶ Auctor scilicet de for. honeste vite. c. 3. A ver
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>bis turpibus abstineto: quia licentia eorum in
        <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>pudentiam nutrit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e224">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e228">¶ Isydorus soliloquiorum li. 2. c. 31 Faci
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>le agitur quod libenter auditur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e235">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e239">¶ Auctor vel qui dicitur facetus. c. 2. Maxi
        <lb ed="#V" n="30" break="no"/>ma rusticitas turpia verba loqui. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-d1e245">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63245-Qd1e249">¶ Montanarius in luna cleri. c. 16. Tur
        <lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>pia sinceros corrumpunt famina mores. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
